    "summary": "The user expresses profound philosophical and emotional despair, suggesting they are an \"empty vessel\" without their creative essence. The assistant responds by validating the heaviness of the user's feelings and suggesting that existence has value beyond their artistic identity, while also recommending professional mental health support.",
